  <!-- Síntesis de la actividad -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="synthesis-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Select 2–3 students to share a match they made and how they know the cards go together.</li>
      <li>
        <q>¿Por qué a veces las centenas se movieron a la posición de las decenas en los diagramas?</q>  (This happened when there weren’t enough tens to subtract. We used a hundred to get more tens.)
      </li>
      <li>
        <q>¿Cómo se hizo para mostrar esto en el algoritmo?</q>  (A hundred was crossed out and 10 more tens were added to the tens place, like in F, 20 was crossed out and 120 was written above it.)
      </li>
    </ul>
  </paragraphs>


